title: Sound On: Budget Deadline And Omicron Concerns
itunes:title: Sound On: Budget Deadline And Omicron Concerns
description:
Guests: Jack Fitzpatrick, Congressional Reporter with Bloomberg Government, Bill Hoagland, Senior Vice President at the Bipartisan Policy Institute, Congressman Warren Davidson, U.S. Representative for Ohio's 8th Congressional District, George Seay, Co-Founder and Chairman of Annandale Capital, Jeanne Sheehan Zaino, Professor at Iona College and Bloomberg Contributor, and Dr. Patrice Harris, former-President of the American Medical Association and CEO of eMed.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
